name: Eclipse, the Astral Sovereign
text: Eclipse's transformation was whispered in legend, a metamorphosis from harbinger to ruler, from Cosmic Harbinger to Astral Sovereign. Now radiant, commanding galaxies, its dominion was absolute. Those who had once feared Eclipse watched in reverence as it sculpted the heavens with a mere flick of its celestial wings.
